edge: Tiger Shroff plays the character of Manav Roy, also known as Munna Michael in this movie.
Siddharth Nigam portrays the character of Young Manav in the initial stages of the movie.
Nawazuddin Siddiqui essays the role of Mahender Fauji in the movie.
Nidhhi Agerwal is cast as Deepika 'Dolly' Sharma in the movie.
Ronit Roy portrays the character of Manasva 'Michael' Roy, Munna's father and caretaker.
Pankaj Tripathi plays the character of Ballo in the movie.
Sudesh Lehri portrays the character of Inspector Shinde in the movie.
Samir Kochhar is cast as Ramesh in the movie.
Gulzar Dastur plays the character of Billo Aunty in the movie.
Farah Khan makes a cameo appearance as Judge of Dancing Star in the movie.
Shaan also has a cameo appearance as Judge of Dancing Star in the movie.
Chitrangada Singh makes a cameo appearance as Judge of Dancing Star in the movie.
Pallavi Kulkarni appears in a cameo role in the movie.
